How to reset password (company specific)
Verify user (EX: Identity IQ, Employee Search Tool, etc)
Advise client to be connected to company VPN, network, etc. 
Issue temporary password
Advise client to enter temporary password
Advise client to set account password according to their department/company requirements (typically will be able to be searched in knowledge base or in active directory)
Advise client to see if they are able to be signed into device 
Advise client to lock screen to ensure passwords sync (Make sure client does not open applications as this can cause password sync issues)
Client will be able to sign in and use applications like normal
